MATCH (u:User)-[:PLACED]->(o:Order)         WHERE datetime(o.created_at) >= datetime() - duration({days:30})         WITH u, COUNT(o) AS orders_last_30d         WHERE orders_last_30d > 0         RETURN u.id            AS id,                orders_last_30d AS orders_last_30d         ORDER BY id         LIMIT 500;
